- Data analysis tool

- analyze your business application logs

- a fully managed elasticsearch service

- aws setup the cluster for you

- Elasticsearch environment
  - Master Nodes
  - Data Nodes

- integrates with
  - Logstash
  - filebeats
  - cloudwatch
  - Kibana
  - Lambda

- Based on the open source ES tech

- Deployment Best pRcatices
 - Deployment types
   - production
   - devlopment and testing
   - Custom

- It is best practice to deploy 3 master and data nodes in 3 azs


